divs: Sighting DetailsWas outside for lunar eclipse that morning with uncle.Decided to look up at stars to see how bright they where.When I looked for orin i notced lights above trees.I started filming to the batterys ran out for no reason.Worked at the Atl airport for over 5 years.It wasnt an airplane just lights is all I could see.
